oblem in an annular domain, a potential flow past a rotating symmetric\nairfoil, and an inviscid transonic compressible flow past a non-symmetric\nairfoil, to demonstrate the effectiveness of our method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jan 2021 17:49:10 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 3 May 2021 12:35:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-05-04"}
