d in this paper provide\nadditional evidence of the presence of MPI in pp collisions, and they can be\nuseful for a better understanding of the heavy-ion-like behaviour observed in\npp data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jan 2021 17:56:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Mar 2021 22:54:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-15"}
