ed by symmetry in spite of the breakdown of the\nassumption of homogeneity and raises the question of why heterogeneity\ndestabilizes some symmetry predicted states, but not others.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jan 2021 21:48:17 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 26 Feb 2021 21:06:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-02"}
