 numerical\nresults to corroborate the proposed numerical properties, including the\nnonlinear stability, robustness under large deformation, and the stress\naccuracy resolved by the higher-order elements.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 25 Jan 2021 22:01:14 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Feb 2021 15:19:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-08-12"}
