s whose morphology cannot be easily explained only\nin the context of the rotation velocity scenario, the threshold limit should be\nat least ~ 20 km/s.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 26 Jan 2021 12:46:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-03"}
